---
title: "Alert Component"
---

# Alert

A static alert banner for displaying contextual messages.

## Properties

| Property | Type | Default | Description |
|----------|------|---------|-------------|
| `type` | `'info' \| 'warning' \| 'error' \| 'success'` | `info` | Controls the color scheme and label |

## Examples

### Info (default)

{% alert type="info" %}
This is an informational alert. Use it to surface neutral context.
{% /alert %}

### Warning

{% alert type="warning" %}
This is a warning alert. Something needs your attention.
{% /alert %}

### Error

{% alert type="error" %}
This is an error alert. Something went wrong.
{% /alert %}

### Success

{% alert type="success" %}
This is a success alert. The operation completed.
{% /alert %}
